snippet.title: Flock - Gameplay Walkthrough | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Flock is a multiplayer co-op game about the joy of flight and collecting adorable flying creatures with your friends. Soar through beautiful landscapes, seeking out rare and elusive creatures to add to your flock. Pip and Richard from the dev team talk about what to expect in this gameplay walkthrough! Coming soon to PS5 and PS4. 

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games
